Items.r: 象有月夜朝夕晝夜，數呈寒暑春夏秋冬。{p}天地定位，乾坤定矣；陰陽相摩相盪，萬物生矣。
Items.c: 象有月夜朝夕晝夜,數呈寒暑春夏秋冬。天地定位,乾坤定矣；陰陽相摩相盪,萬物生矣。
Items.mt: The elephant has the moon and the night, the day and the night, the number is cold, summer, spring, summer, autumn and winter. When the sky and the earth are positioned, the heaven and the earth are fixed; when the yin and the yang are in harmony with each other, all things are born.
